name: New Year's Duo (Individuals)
description:
New Year's Duo here you pick one or the other and they are Countdown to 2014 and Kiss Me At Midnight. Countdown to 2014 is shown in 2 coats but you can always do 3 coats, and Kiss Me At Midnight is shown in 3 coats. 

Countdown to 2014 has a milky white base and is full of different size, shape and color of glitters. You can find gold & silver stars, large dots in turquoise, pink, violet and blue, small hexes in blue, pink, red, orange, purple, gold, silver and fine green and micro pink. It's basically a party in a bottle ready for the party on your nails as you say bye bye to 2013!!! 

Kiss Me At Midnight has a red base it's a jelly but has good coverage in 3 coats. It has gold holo in squares, dots and hex glitter very pretty!! And we thought of that special first kiss of the new year when naming and making this pretty polish. So put this baby and start the new year off right!! 

Item comes in a full glass bottle (15ml.) or a mini glass bottle (5ml). All of our products are 3 free, which means it does not contain toluene, formaldehyde, and dibutyl ph

name: Monster's in the Closet (Individuals)
description:
Monster's in the Closet is back as a Limited Edition to celebrate our 1st birthday of being in business!!! Yes as of Dec 15th it will be 1 year since we opened up, and we decided to give our first collection a make over and bring them back and here they are. 
This Collection is inspired by Monster's Inc

Kitty!! Is inspired by Sulley and we named it Kitty!! because Boo calls him that. This polish has a pale blue crelly that has blue, purple and silver holo hex glitter in different sizes and small purple bar glitter because of Sulley's fur.

One Eyed Monster is inspired by Mike who's green so why not make a green glitter bomb. This is just glitter so it has no base color it's full of matte pastel green, holo green glitter and a little of iridescent hex glitter. Layer it over a base color or use it on it's own still a cute glitter bomb!!

Peek A Boo is inspired by Boo and her purple monster costume.  This one has a purple jelly base and is full of large and medium holo purple dots, silver and lavender holo hex glitter. Cute and girly just like boo!!

Item comes in a full glass bottle (15ml.) or a mini glass bottle (5ml). All of our products are 3 free, which means it does not contain toluene, formaldehyde, and dibutyl ph

name: Wintertime Collection (Individuals)
description:
This is our Wintertime Collection with 5 different and beautiful polishes. Not just for the holidays but good for all winter long and some even after that. Swatches are all 3 coats.

Frozen is a light blue crelly with matte white fine, small and snowflake glitter and micro silver holo glitter to give it that extra little sparkle.

Peppermints has a white milky base with fine red holo glitter and micro silver holo glitter. Simple yet so pretty!!

Sweater Weather has a milky nude base along with red holo fine, small hex and medium dot glitter. Reminds us of the kind of warm sweaters people wear during this time of the year because  of the weather, a beautiful nude.

Ice Queen has a white milky base and is full of blue and and turquoise fine & small hex glitter and short bar glitter. This icy queen is a must have for winter.

Frostbitten has a blue jelly base and is full of silver holo fine, small, medium dots and snowflake glitter along with blue hexes. This one is truly gorgeous it can be worn alone for the jelly look or layered over a dark base for depth.

Item comes in a full glass bottle (15ml.) or a mini glass bottle (5ml). All of our products are 3 free, which means it does not contain toluene, formaldehyde, and dibutyl phthalate.

name: Gift Certificate
description:
Don't know what to get someone as a gift? 
Can't go wrong with a gift certificate!! They make for great stocking stuffers for the holidays

Here you can purchase a gift certificate for a Birthday, Christmas, graduation or just because. We have so many polishes to pick from that this makes it easier if you have someone who is picky. 

We we mail you the code the next business day, or you can print it at home just leave a message on your order so we know what you prefer, if no instructions are given we will automatically sent it out the next business day by mail. Also if you want it to say something specific like HAPPY BIRTHDAY, MERRY CHRISTMAS or whatever it is please also leave this in the instruction. 

**U.S mailing address only, next business day means Monday - Friday**
